# Revision history for Gisdatigo

Very opinionated automation for most of the gem update process for Rails applications managed with bundler.

## Unreleased

## v0.4.0 - 24/05/2022

* Add CLI

## v0.3.2 - 07/06/2020

* Fix release mistakes (sorry)

## v0.3.1 - 07/06/2020

* Fix git reset
* Fix changes being listed in `git status` but that were already commited

## v0.3.0 - 01/05/2018

* Run bundle update with conservative flag
* Run two updates with different options

## v0.2.1 - 01/05/2018

* Fix release mistakes (sorry)

## v0.2.0 - 01/05/2018

* Restrict codeclimate-test-reporter version
* Target development for ruby 2.5.1
* Update rake
* Update mocha
* Replace factory_girl by factory_bot
* Replace git gem by rugged

## v0.1.0 - 30/01/2016

* Ignore coverage report for railtie
* Gem version requirements relaxed
* Update development Ruby version to 2.3.0
* Accept test_command configuration

## v0.0.1 - 22/09/2015

* Updates through `bundle update`
* Automated test run
* Automated rollback upon test failure after update
* Remaining outdated list production
